::Striker::

Striker flies backwards, the wind pushing him. He nearly yelps as he hits the 
spike, his momentuum driving it through his abominal area. His jetpack going 
the other way, he flies slowly forward, sliding off the spike, his systems 
screaming at him as mechfluid flows freely, and at dangerous amounts, out of 
the wound.

Striker continues firing at Savage, his aim becoming worse, even though a bot 
Savage's size wasn't that hard to aim at.
